<!--
Example (delete me):

## Rule: Never mock the payments gateway in integration tests

Status: active
Source: failure
Scope: directory
Applies to:
- tests/integration/payments/**

Rule:
- Integration tests under tests/integration/payments/ must run against
  the sandbox payments API, never a mock or stub.

Rationale:
- A mocked gateway passed tests twice while the real sandbox contract had
  changed, causing two production incidents (see failure-log.md,
  2026-01-14 and 2026-02-03).

Examples:
- Do: call the sandbox client configured via PAYMENTS_SANDBOX_URL.
- Do not: import unittest.mock.patch for the payments client in this
  directory.

Validation:
- npm run test:integration -- payments (must hit the sandbox, verified by
  checking the request log for a sandbox host).
-->

